snippet.title: Johnjohn  - Solo Dolo feat. Koala
snippet.description:
JohnJohn X Koala - Solo Dolo M/V

Bobblehead Music presents their first single "Solo Dolo" featuring artists "JohnJohn" and "Koala". All raised in the Southern California region bringing that Cali style music back to their home country so that the people can experience and enjoy a new type of style in the hip hop genre.

Listen here:  Available on all music platforms
--
Camera Director: Starfield Kambo
PD: Angelina Kang
